		<div id="comment_body_64284554"><p>I asked Copilot to summarize a pdf I'd written myself about some life-story stuff on storyworth, and it started doing an ok job, then made up a complete nonsense story about me going to Amsterdam, meeting the woman who would eventually be my wife there while we had lots of fun, including running from the cops.</p><p>Not even faintly true, nor could that be inferred from anything I wrote.<br>It did get my wife's name right.</p></div>
	</div>

